  "title": "poc(chat): add product modal with navigation",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\n[FX-3510](https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-3510)\r\n\r\nThis PoC:\r\n- Adds an interactive product modal that displays detailed product information when the carousel action is clicked.\r\n- Implements keyboard navigation support (arrow keys to navigate between products and the Escape key to close).\r\n- Includes action buttons for viewing product details and adding products to favorites.\r\n- Adds animations and transitions for modal interactions.\r\n- Ensures the design is responsive.\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"350\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/884d822e-2112-4178-8000-444e0bf8a327\" />\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1476\" height=\"792\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b13423ec-fa74-4d3f-8d62-23273d5ef463\" />\r\n\n\n[FX-3510]: https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-3510?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNWRkNTljNzYxNjVmNDY3MDlhMDU5Y2ZhYzA5YTRkZjUiLCJwIjoiZ2l0aHViLWNvbS1KU1cifQ",
